org.finra.herd.service.helper

Class DefaultNotificationMessageBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.finra.herd.service.helper.DefaultNotificationMessageBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NotificationMessageBuilder

    @Component
public class DefaultNotificationMessageBuilder
extends Object
implements NotificationMessageBuilder
    Default implementation of the builder for notification messages. Constructs an ESB message based on given data. To use a different implementation overwrite the bean defined in ServiceSpringModuleConfig.sqsMessageBuilder().
